---
title: Smart Sage Turkey Patties and Cranberry Sauce with Sweet Potatoes and Broccoli
description: Warm fall flavours with sage, turkey and sweet potatoes, smothered in a cranberry sauce is the perfect dinner! Like putting on a cozy sweater.
